Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Lion of Talisid level 1.
Specifics: At every level, the Lion of Talisid progresses in one selected divine spellcasting class. If a character had more than one spellcasting class in which she could cast spells before she became a Lion of Talsid, the player must decide which class to assign each level of Lion of Talsid for the purpose of determining spells per day and spells known.
Use: Automatic.